e Lotus Stra as in certain Buddha-realms.The myriads of "thoughts", or moments in a single day and night, each with its consequences of good and evil; probably 8,400,000,000 is meant.The 华严经 Hua-yen stra, as delivered at eight assemblies.The classification or grades of disciples according to the Tiantai 圆教 perfect teaching, i.e. (1) 观行 grade of the five classes, or stages, of lay disciples; (2) 相似 grade of the ten classes of or ordinary monks and nuns; above these are the 分bodhisattva stages of those progressing towards Buddhahood i.e.　(3) 十住, (4) 十行, (5) 十向, (6) 十地, (7) 等觉, and (8) the perfect or Buddha stage 究竟, i.e. 妙觉. Cf. 六.The eight stages of the human foetus: 羯罗蓝 kalala, the appearance after the first week from conception; 额部昙 arbuda, at end of second week; 闭尸 pe, third; 健南 ghana, fourth; 罗奢法 prakh, limbs formed during fifth week; sixth, hair, nails, and teeth; seventh, the organs of sense, eyes, ears, nose, and tongue; and eighth, complete formation.Eight Buddhas of the eastern quarter.v. 八倒.
