r 烦恼 the passions and delusions, etc.The retribution of transmigrational-bondage.The bondage of unenlightenment.Bondage; to bind; also the 十缠 and 四缚 q.v.To repair, put in order, white out, copy.<term lang="sa">janma-maraa</term>, 生死 birth and death.<term lang="sa">jantu</term>, 生 all living being; also 禅豆; 缮头; 缮兜.Broken; deficient, lacking; a vacancy, a post.A breach and leakage, a breach of the discipline.<term lang="sa">jla</term>. A net, a web.The 'eyes', or meshes of a net. For the <title>Brahmajla stra</title> v. 梵网经.<term lang="sa">kukkua</term> is a cock, or fowl; this is intp. As the clucking of fowls: cf. 究 and 拘.
